<h3 id="section">安装环境</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Mac自带git 可以升级下 省略git</li>
  <li>Ruby环境的<a href="https://github.com/ruby-china/ruby-china/wiki/Mac-OS-X-%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-Ruby">安装</a></li>
</ul>

